<p>But what if the bias that youve detected seems to be for an entire group of people? Maybe you notice that your call center in the Southern US has transcripts that are consistently of poorer quality than call centers in other parts of the country. Because this looks like a systematic problem, rather than a one-off problem, youll probably want to take some kind of action to address this bias.</p>
